title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Mar 10 2022

description:
Listen in as GOP Rep. Maria Salazar wants no-fly zone, can't explain what it will mean. Sen. Menendez against a no-fly zone. C&B take calls. Where's Fauci? Bill Roggio, Senior Fellow at the Foundation for Defense of Democracies and editor of the Long War Journal, brings us what's happening on the ground in Ukraine. Disney CEO wants to talk gay issues with DeSantis, Disney uses ESPN to push lies about Florida sex bill.
